<div id="popup_welcome_container" class="tcenter standard_popup_container">
    <div class="standard_popup welcome_popup">
        <div class="title_wide_popup">Welcome to ShareBloc!</div>
        <div class="standard_popup_content">
                Thanks for joining ShareBloc! Here are some tips to getting started.
                <br><br>
                <div class="welcome_popup_list">
                    <span class="list_point_title">1. Read and vote on the content shared by like-minded professionals.</span>
                    <br>
                    We curated a newsfeed for you from other professionals with similar interests. You can vote on the quality of the content or comment on it.
                    <br><br>
                    <span class="list_point_title">2. Submit the stuff you want to read.</span>
                    <br>
                    We know you read a lot of great things and sometimes you want to <a href="/post/" target="_blank">share it with others</a> in your profession. You can also <a href="/post/question" target="_blank">ask questions</a> to the community.
                    <br><br>
                    <span class="list_point_title">3. Read our guidelines.</span>
                    <br>
                    We have <a href="/guidelines/" target="_blank">ShareBloc etiquette</a> that we hope you follow. Thank you.
                    <br><br>
                </div>
                You can let others know you joined ShareBloc by sharing on Twitter. Thank you for joining our community!
        </div>
        <div class="popup_function">
            <a id="welcome_popup_close" class="save_changes" href="#">Got it!</a>
            <a href='#' data-provider="twitter"
                 data-text="Join me and thousands of others in @ShareBloc, a community for professionals to share business content that matters. {$base_url}/invite/{$user_info.code_name}"
                 class="share_post_btn cancel">
                <img class="tweet_img" src="/images/twitter.png">&nbsp;Share on Twitter
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>